%pyspark
import pyjake.basemodule
from pyjake.sparkmodule import udf_dt2dh, udf_floatize

uvi = spark.read.parquet('hdfs:///nl/kma/uvi_10min.parquet')

# 안면도만 고르기
uvi = uvi.where('station_code = 132')\
         .withColumn('datehour', udf_dt2dh('date', 'time'))\
         .withColumn('tuvi', udf_floatize('tuvi'))\
         .select('datehour', 'tuvi')\
         .groupby('datehour').sum('tuvi')\
         .withColumnRenamed('sum(tuvi)', 'tuvi').sort('datehour')
uvi.show()

%pyspark
from pyjake.sparkmodule import udf_floatize, udf_intize

pm_loc_near_anmyeon = spark.read.parquet('hdfs:///pm/airkorea/pm_loc_near_anmyeon.parquet')
pm_loc_near_anmyeon = pm_loc_near_anmyeon\
        .withColumn('station_code', udf_intize('station_code'))\
        .withColumn('lat', udf_floatize('lat'))\
        .withColumn('lon', udf_floatize('lon'))
pm_loc_near_anmyeon.show()
pm_loc_near_anmyeon.printSchema()

paragraphs.title: join station code
paragraphs.text:
%pyspark

def get_subset(spdf_target, station_code):
    subset = spdf_target.where('station_code = %d' % station_code)\
                        .select('datehour', 'pm10', 'pm25')
    subset = subset.withColumnRenamed('pm10', 'pm10_' + str(station_code))\
                   .withColumnRenamed('pm25', 'pm25_' + str(station_code))
    return subset

station_code_rows = pm_near_anmyeon.select('station_code').distinct().collect()
stcode_list = list(map(lambda r: r['station_code'], station_code_rows))
print('station codes near Anmyeon:', stcode_list)

uvpm_anmyeon = get_subset(pm_near_anmyeon, stcode_list[0])
for i in range(1, len(stcode_list)):
    uvpm_anmyeon = uvpm_anmyeon.join(get_subset(pm_near_anmyeon, stcode_list[i]), 'datehour')

uvpm_anmyeon = uvpm_anmyeon.sort('datehour')
uvpm_anmyeon.show()

%pyspark
from pyjake.basemodule import udf_dt2d

uvpm_anmyeon_daily = uvpm_anmyeon.withColumn('date', udf_dt2d('datehour'))\
                           .groupby('date')\
                           .agg({'pm10_534491':'sum',
                                 'pm25_534491':'sum',
                                 'pm10_534422':'sum',
                                 'pm25_534422':'sum',
                                 'pm10_534461':'sum',
                                 'pm25_534461':'sum',
                                 'pm10_534463':'sum',
                                 'pm25_534463':'sum',
                                 'tuvi': 'avg'
                           })

uvpm_anmyeon_daily.show()

%pyspark
from pyjake.basemodule import udf_dt2d

uvpm_anmyeon_daily = uvpm_anmyeon_daily.withColumnRenamed('avg(tuvi)', 'UVI')\
                        .withColumnRenamed('sum(pm10_534491)', 'pm10_534491')\
                        .withColumnRenamed('sum(pm25_534491)', 'pm25_534491')\
                        .withColumnRenamed('sum(pm10_534422)', 'pm10_534422')\
                        .withColumnRenamed('sum(pm25_534422)', 'pm25_534422')\
                        .withColumnRenamed('sum(pm10_534461)', 'pm10_534461')\
                        .withColumnRenamed('sum(pm25_534461)', 'pm25_534461')\
                        .withColumnRenamed('sum(pm10_534463)', 'pm10_534463')\
                        .withColumnRenamed('sum(pm25_534463)', 'pm25_534463')
uvpm_anmyeon_daily.show()
uvpm_anmyeon_daily.createOrReplaceTempView('uvpm_anmyeon_daily')

%sql

select date, UVI / 40 * 1000, pm10_534491, pm10_534422, pm10_534461, pm10_534463 from uvpm_anmyeon_daily

%pyspark
from pyjake.basemodule import udf_dt2d

uvpm_anmyeon_daily = uvpm_anmyeon.withColumn('date', udf_dt2d('datehour'))\
                           .groupby('date')\
                           .agg({'pm10_534491':'sum',
                                 'pm25_534491':'sum',
                                 'pm10_534422':'sum',
                                 'pm25_534422':'sum',
                                 'pm10_534461':'sum',
                                 'pm25_534461':'sum',
                                 'pm10_534463':'sum',
                                 'pm25_534463':'sum',
                                 'tuvi': 'sum'
                           })

uvpm_anmyeon_daily.show()

%pyspark
from pyjake.basemodule import udf_dt2d

uvpm_anmyeon_daily = uvpm_anmyeon_daily.withColumnRenamed('sum(tuvi)', 'UVI')\
                        .withColumnRenamed('sum(pm10_534491)', 'pm10_534491')\
                        .withColumnRenamed('sum(pm25_534491)', 'pm25_534491')\
                        .withColumnRenamed('sum(pm10_534422)', 'pm10_534422')\
                        .withColumnRenamed('sum(pm25_534422)', 'pm25_534422')\
                        .withColumnRenamed('sum(pm10_534461)', 'pm10_534461')\
                        .withColumnRenamed('sum(pm25_534461)', 'pm25_534461')\
                        .withColumnRenamed('sum(pm10_534463)', 'pm10_534463')\
                        .withColumnRenamed('sum(pm25_534463)', 'pm25_534463')
uvpm_anmyeon_daily.show()
uvpm_anmyeon_daily.createOrReplaceTempView('uvpm_anmyeon_daily')
